39:16.225 --> 39:19.098
To support him, or to see
where he was in his career.

39:19.099 --> 39:21.848
Because his success wasn't complete

39:21.849 --> 39:24.432
unless we could enjoy it with him.

39:24.433 --> 39:26.349
And Jimmy liked us around,

39:26.350 --> 39:29.390
