39:36.058 --> 39:38.517
She was smart. She was gorgeous.

39:41.099 --> 39:42.349
She was a lawyer

39:42.350 --> 39:44.516
from Cambridge University in England

39:44.517 --> 39:46.557
and Hastings and Berkeley.

39:46.558 --> 39:48.641
And, yeah, she was a Playboy centerfold.

39:48.642 --> 39:50.973
But I like strong personality women.

39:50.974 --> 39:52.224
I like women that have an idea

39:52.225 --> 39:53.265
of how they want to live

39:53.266 --> 39:55.140
and what they want to do.

39:55.141 --> 39:57.474
And she was incredible.

39:57.475 --> 39:58.932
I was at a party,

39:58.933 --> 40:01.848
and there was Jimmy,
and he followed me out,

40:01.849 --> 40:03.641
And he said, "If you give
me your phone number,

40:03.642 --> 40:05.848
and I remember it, can I call you?"

40:05.849 --> 40:08.766
He called me about
10 times the next day,

40:08.767 --> 40:10.766
and he asks me on a date.

40:10.767 --> 40:13.807
And when it was the appointed hour,

40:13.808 --> 40:17.682
