45:21.433 --> 45:24.641
by saying that
I financialize his dreams.

45:24.642 --> 45:28.349
- But probably that's what I do.
- And playback!

45:41.225 --> 45:42.682
Yo, yo, yo!

45:42.683 --> 45:44.848
Yo, we in the house. Eazy and Dr. Dre's

45:44.849 --> 45:46.432
