45:46.433 --> 45:48.058
and we drunk as a motherfucker.

45:50.099 --> 45:52.098
♪ That appetite is tremendous ♪

45:52.099 --> 45:53.682
♪ So I'm gonna spin this ♪

45:53.683 --> 45:55.349
♪ Drop up some violence because
